|---|---|
| Define a GET-only route | `route("/path", { get: () => <Page /> })` |
| Define multi-method route | `route("/api/x", { get: handler1, post: handler2, delete: handler3 })` |
| Define custom HTTP method | `route("/path", { custom: { report: handler } })` |
| Disable auto-OPTIONS | `route("/path", { get: handler, config: { disableOptions: true } })` |
| Disable auto-405 | `route("/path", { get: handler, config: { disable405: true } })` |
| Custom OPTIONS handler | `route("/path", { get: handler, custom: { options: handler }, config: { disableOptions: true } })` |
| Middleware per method | `route("/path", { get: [auth, handler], post: [auth, adminCheck, handler] })` |
| Global middleware | top-level functions in `defineApp([...])` array |
| Layout wrapping | `layout(MyLayout, [route(...), route(...)])` |
| Document + SSR config | `render(Document, [route(...)], { rscPayload: true, ssr: true })` |
| Path prefixing | `prefix("/blog", blogRoutes)` |
| Error handling | `except((error, requestInfo) => <ErrorPage />)` |

